Python users: pip install plotly==4.0.0
Definitely excited to use the updated Plotly.py. This shift to offline-only is amazing. It &ldquo;requires no internet connection, no account, no authentication tokens, and no payment of any kind.&rdquo; Great stuff here, and now Plotly Express comes built in to make interactive plot making even easier&hellip; &ldquo;plotly.express is to plotly what seaborn is to matplotlib&rdquo;
For you Jupyter and Colab fans, rendering Plotly figures to these notebooks (and other IDEs) should now feel a lot less clunky.
